coldpool 3.3-1 (November 13, 2023)
----------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURE

- Added kriging_loocv() function to compare kriging methods 
  using leave-one-out cross-validation for ordinary kriging, 
  co-kriging, and regression kriging methods, with or without
  anisotropy. 
- Added estimate_anisotropy() function for estimating 2D
  anisotropy in variograms using k-fold cross-validation.